Subject: [PATCH] Remove lalsuite requirement

In conda this project can explicitly depend on the component packages that are actually needed
---
 setup.py | 1 -
 1 file changed, 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/setup.py b/setup.py
index 8925589..d55330c 100644
--- a/setup.py
+++ b/setup.py
@@ -40,7 +40,6 @@ setup(name=PACKAGENAME,
       install_requires=[
           'gpstime',
           'igwn-auth-utils',
-          'lalsuite',
           'ligo-segments',
           'lscsoft-glue>=3.0.1,<4.0.0',
           'pyOpenSSL>=0.14',
